      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/47e85d/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2022-02-17T09:26:21.087Z",
      "cooked": "<p>As I think, my workouts are saved on the server, so you can track them, for example, the one I did on 02/15/2022, where for 98 minutes I had a premeditated cadence of 75 rpm.</p>\n<p>Shifting to a slightly higher / lower wheel speed does not help much. And after switching to an even higher / lower  gear ratio and maintaining the set cadence in training, the result is a permanent increased / reduced training power, higher / lower than the set one.</p>",
